634
00:40:54,600 --> 00:40:56,599
So, I let him off the hook.

635
00:40:56,600 --> 00:40:59,340
I went to Quan Guanqing.

636
00:40:59,340 --> 00:41:01,199
After sleeping with him for three days,

637
00:41:01,200 --> 00:41:03,879
