666
00:42:36,800 --> 00:42:40,000
Back then, I wanted to kill Duan Zhengchun.

667
00:42:41,040 --> 00:42:44,780
So, I framed you for it.

668
00:42:50,320 --> 00:42:55,519
A'Zhu's death is on you, too.

669
